hopobject.body: Will I be paid weekly or monthly? south berkeley pharmacy Celebs aren't afraid to get a little sexy when it comes to ad campaigns. Whether they're flaunting their curves in sizzling lingerie or showing off their modeling chops in sultry high-fashion shoots, these celebrities are so hot you'll forget what it is exactly they're trying to sell. Check out the sexiest star advertisements ... Season 12 of "Project Runway" is right around the corner, and if this eye-popping promotional ad is any indication, it's going to be the sexiest go-around yet. Heidi Klum and Tim Gunn definitely have a "make it work" moment as they pose glamorously in over-the-top outfits while naked models fawn at their feet -- but is the billboard too sexy? It's already been banned in Los Angeles for containing too much nudity. The Lifetime series' racy ad is still slated to arrive in New York where it will run on buses and billboards.
